My return to skip writing after I was a one hit wonder with draft swap.

This started out as a draft from plaguebearer, who deserves all the credit for the core concept of a plant Denny's that grows when people shit in parking lots, and the title. Everything else was just me following the logic of Denny's-as-flowering-plant until I found the madness within.

I did much of the writing for this on my phone with the flu, so, yeah.

So many people did crit and review on this, so I've very probably missed someone. If I missed you, I'm sorry I suck, let me know and I'll put you in and write you a two line poem of apology or something.

So, thanks to:

TheManhattenProject and to the people I missed. And to you, the reader!





