Needlessly convoluted setup for what the payout is.

I mean, I really enjoyed the observation log, don't get me wrong, but for all the detail in how it propagates, it loses out in efficiency, for how much those traits mean very little in the end.

This could have simply been the single weird location; lumping on multiple fantastical traits lessened its legitimacy and strained immersion for me.







